 "summary": "The API surface is minimal for the roadmap Stage 0.4 target: `Deck p` as a `Subgroup` with `mem_iff`, `map_proj`, `fiberHomeomorph` plus apply/symm lemmas, and `smul_eq_apply` to bridge the subgroup-transferred action. `HomeomorphAction.lean` supplies only the necessary `MulAction`/`FaithfulSMul`/`ContinuousConstSMul` instances and the subgroup `ContinuousConstSMul` transfer. No `@[expose]` annotations; `@[simp]` annotations are on the correct normal-form lemmas and none would loop or fire wrongly.",
